data.description: Welcome to this updated 3/2 ranch located on a large corner lot in the Oakley Township subdivision. At almost 1900 square feet of living space this home offers an open concept floor plan. The main living area offers an electric fireplace with hardwood floors throughout, including a large eat-in kitchen with white cabinets and stainless steel appliances. Off of the main living area the home offers a flex space that can be utilized as a formal dining room, home office, or home gym, the possibilities are endless. After a long day, retire to the large owner's suite to relax. The owner's suite boasts trey ceilings, bathroom with a spa style tub, and a linen closet. The home includes generous secondary bedrooms with spacious closets that share a guest bath. Step out onto the rear patio to enjoy a private evening in the enclosed backyard. As an added bonus, the home comes equipped with closed circuit security cameras covering the entire perimeter of the property. **NOTE: Seller is offering an allowance to paint exterior of home. See private remarks.**
